0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":3,\"relative_time_description\":\"10 個月前\",\"text\":\"先說結論，短期內不會再去了，\\n三顆星給從前的甘泉魚麵。\\n-\\n內部整修了好久，終於等到八月，\\n甘泉的內裝變得很美式復古的感覺，\\n裝潢和產品完全不搭，\\n這種裝潢比較適合美式餐點（披薩漢堡之類的）或咖啡廳。\\n\\n再來是價錢和味道，\\n新菜單十分花俏，\\n只注意到平常常點的品項──東北酸菜白肉麵，\\n稍稍漲了五塊錢（$150->$155）。\\n內容物的部分，\\n不知是否颱風影響，\\n以前酸菜白肉麵會有滿滿高麗菜和小白菜，現在只剩酸白菜、洋蔥和豆苗（？）\\n凍豆腐也由兩塊方形變成一塊方型切一半，\\n整體份量縮水不少。\\n湯頭部分，以往湯頭鮮甜，酸度也恰到好處，現在只剩下鹹味，\\n連單吃酸白菜都只有鹹味、沒有酸味。\\n肉片的狀態也不太對，但我說不上來。\\n\\n結帳時得知業主換人，所以以前的集點卡不能用了，換成貴賓卡，\\n新的貴賓卡可以贈送飲料，\\n嗯但，\\n今天點了奶茶，喝起來水水的，\\n如果還要花菜單上標價 $40，真的會生氣欸:(\\n經營權換人，能否連配方一起買了呢？(´･ω･`)\\n\\n（第一張圖片為今日用餐的酸菜白肉麵，其他麵是舊的甘泉）\",\"time\":1723048586,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"YHsiang\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103168072870599053533/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS2bAXZ0ky5wMJxAcKOUHZ1dLpbmylc5Y_RUWezaAZeBXEDV9O=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":2,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 週前\",\"text\":\"第一次看到麵裡面放高麗菜絲，神奇\",\"time\":1748511043,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNT_HsrXIpzZLGem43HAZfR_GPvF_IiDT3gs1ifpA1Ua4HEryq1sC_Wti6KVMx_bmQ4daLvOAZLwuNfEFUo4U-bl7Xntq7ntS_0GOtQhAZl1kUDj-GpZwu_YxYF4-ydFLfQwMKkT99dWdKyC0-nsDeXm7wQ_WF5jwtzX6pZIUQ1SJhptaTAlrTaNf9QfRlPG8bvYrKUhCx18CshizUb3EdmaFk7-LhOyCWqwxH8PXrMYO98HR9R_aRjUb6Zh1YKSzUO8-M8IHlR56ynd_VgaCNjzN8GqlHj9Ru2JwDiraL1VIo23jgOTSqs9TZ3NRw_D4rtI41M6E_f1byv2ufN2wEbDl0h4U5Fc5UQ9UWAokkc-1HEdJyxtRxWBZ9Qitf5mpURY7VDkP6emLcqhrRLaZJlKPT_CFMT5zgPXz_adzds1YTzMUIKuM-bYsczuNR5O1TQI6FdggCTSsgVign7UpliUcXOTQeMh2FLgBMS0-Pal96pRDHHuictfTncxEq5-1_eavZqSdTxVRyMzUht9X-n9SDOceHHuZH-M4Ob_gojuLeyrSOXi6yuCp--hEJ9BP8jMZbuc5jkEFN5D0jPuGNSalWrwQmNXgK9Mauydk8HOOQC0pesixs9ZHQeTQBK4rsAM9B6H\",\"AXQCQNSr2UWcmZy4O3S3oNqQGYWwg2g49kFXXySgKFEjcwm86cKOsFYmL6JA8wIKVs42cnwdFo-nlwCZC1GaXtpVtp7cAD_Rthmrrf6lLRy5ZKjkLk9ODxjYOlUK8PNZq4iXwIQMAhOSGh5ymr0AIxJD0oWbeE2Q5TuRG0mXGpmzJBsp5IaaXk6c6yKZ4IMw-PSSfX5QHXrhGYq7EcI1qzBcoR6W8zX5YHWb_yG_nUujBQVMl6alfrKMl0J62X-z0z5vXijE45VL0s